1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 23=

3
00:01:11,340 --> 00:01:13,700
ظآزA thought in youth's primeظآز

4
00:01:13,700 --> 00:01:15,680
ظآزWe walked together laughingظآز

5
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,920
You know I'm not Rong Zhaohua.

6
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,280
So why?

7
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:21,760
Because

8
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,840
I love you.

9
00:01:25,239 --> 00:01:26,359
Back then,

10
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,640
when you died,

11
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,680
I realized

12
00:01:31,159 --> 00:01:33,519
I had already fallen
for you beyond repair.

13
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:36,519
But we were separated by life and death.

14
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,920
So I buried those feelings

15
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,599
deep in my heart.

16
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,480
Later,

17
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,040
I noticed

18
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:50,120
that the Consort Rong by my side,

19
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,959
her every frown,

20
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,439
every smile,

21
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:56,480
every gesture and movement,

22
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:58,959
was just like you.

23
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:02,020
ظآزCan I still hope that one dayظآز

24
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:04,280
In the dead of night,

25
00:02:04,879 --> 00:02:06,359
I wondered

26
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,520
who it was

27
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,000
that I truly loved.

28
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:12,919
But now I know.

29
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,479
The one I love

30
00:02:17,039 --> 00:02:19,680
has always been the same soul.

31
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:23,340
ظآزA thought in youth's primeظآز

32
00:02:23,340 --> 00:02:24,940
ظآزWe walked together laughingظآز

33
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,000
Don't cry.

34
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:28,080
I'm grateful

35
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:31,280
that before I die,

36
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,599
I get to see you one last time.

37
00:02:34,199 --> 00:02:34,840
I am

38
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,800
truly happy.

39
00:02:37,340 --> 00:02:39,020
ظآزLooking backظآز

40
00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:40,780
ظآزBetween heaven and earthظآز

41
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:44,000
I already let you die once.

42
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,960
I will never,

43
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:50,479
never let you die

44
00:02:50,879 --> 00:02:51,479
a...

45
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:54,240
a...

46
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,280
again.

47
00:02:58,180 --> 00:03:02,380
ظآزIn memories bright and clearظآز

48
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:05,100
ظآزI recall a life beforeظآز

49
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:06,860
ظآزWith no regretsظآز

50
00:03:06,860 --> 00:03:08,420
ظآزFor this chapterظآز

51
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:12,500
ظآزCan I still hope that one dayظآز

52
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,840
Kui.

53
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:16,120
Kill Feng Ye!

54
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:20,340
ظآزCan I still hope that one dayظآز

55
00:03:23,060 --> 00:03:27,420
ظآزWe will meet againظآز

56
00:03:31,039 --> 00:03:31,800
Kui.

57
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:34,000
I once promised you

58
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,919
I would build a new world.

59
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:37,719
We're one step away.

60
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:40,520
Only one person stands in our way.

61
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:41,719
Kill him.

62
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,439
From this day on,

63
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:44,560
the realm will be ours to share.

64
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,120
If you won't act,

65
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,319
then I will.

66
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,639
Sister.

67
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:09,560
This time,

68
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,159
I'm sorry.

69
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,560
You're safe now.

70
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:18,360
I won't let you go back.

71
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,560
But she's my sister.

72
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,279
Just because she's your sister,

73
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,800
you'll stop at nothing to avenge her?

74
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,360
You'll keep risking your life for her?

75
00:05:36,759 --> 00:05:38,000
Do you know

76
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,360
how happy I was when I learned

77
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,720
my sister was alive?

78
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,879
If I didn't know what you told me,

79
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:46,879
I could have stayed happy forever,

80
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:49,120
just being her sister,

81
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:51,199
without ever wondering
if she was using me.

82
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,800
Now that I know everything,

83
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:58,000
how am I supposed to face all of this?

84
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:09,079
But Yukui,

85
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,600
I can't live without you anymore.

86
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,240
I need you.

87
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:20,199
I know my sister was wrong.

88
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:24,639
But I won't give up on her.

89
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,000
No one

90
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,079
deserves to be given up on.

91
00:06:41,319 --> 00:06:42,879
Then are you giving up on me?

92
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,680
Greetings, Your Highness.

93
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:13,519
Greetings, Your Majesty.

94
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:14,480
Lord of Zhenbei's rebellion

95
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,240
and His Majesty's death
have been announced.

96
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,160
The court officials

97
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,439
seem to have some objections.

98
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:22,279
Speak.

99
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:27,879
They say

100
00:07:27,879 --> 00:07:29,639
a treacherous consort
has brought ruin to the realm,

101
00:07:29,759 --> 00:07:30,879
and now that she holds power,

102
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:32,839
Kun will face disaster.

103
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,399
No matter what they say,

104
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,680
I am sitting on this throne.

105
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:40,959
But these people,

106
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,680
kill a few of them,

107
00:07:44,959 --> 00:07:46,279
and the rest will fall in line.

108
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:48,519
Yes.

109
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,120
I'll see to it immediately.

110
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:59,000
She's doing this to force me out.

111
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:01,720
Tomorrow at the execution ground,

112
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,680
I will be there.

113
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:08,240
All of this started because of me.

114
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,839
And I should be the one to end it.

115
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:15,759
My Lord.

116
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,079
I will go with you tomorrow.

117
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:20,959
But

118
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:25,360
what about the Holy Maiden?

119
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,240
She will understand.

120
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,759
What's wrong?

121
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,120
It's not pretty?

122
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,840
Or

123
00:09:22,879 --> 00:09:23,840
you don't like it?

124
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,639
It's pretty,

125
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,879
and I like it.

126
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:35,960
In our Zhao Tribe,

127
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:38,440
the red cord represents
the matchmaker's thread.

128
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:42,080
When you meet someone you truly love,

129
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,720
you tie this red cord

130
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:48,320
around each other's wrists.

131
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:50,480
It's a symbol

132
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:53,120
of never being apart.

133
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,120
What's wrong?

134
00:10:06,399 --> 00:10:07,120
You don't want to?

135
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:11,559
I...

136
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,279
You and I,

137
00:10:16,679 --> 00:10:17,879
through everything we've been through...

138
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,360
I know

139
00:10:21,399 --> 00:10:22,360
